
╔════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║         🔐 OTP Email Backend Server               ║
╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

✅ Server running on http://localhost:3001

📧 Email Service Configuration:
   Provider: Ethereal Email (Free, Test Email)
   SMTP Host: smtp.ethereal.email:587

📌 API Endpoints:
   POST   /api/send-otp      - Send OTP to email
   POST   /api/verify-otp    - Verify OTP code
   POST   /api/resend-otp    - Resend OTP
   GET    /api/otp-status/:email - Check OTP status (debug)
   POST   /api/clear-otps    - Clear all OTPs (debug)
   GET    /api/health        - Server health check

🧪 Test in Browser:
   Open: http://localhost:3000/v1/mfa.html

📚 Documentation:
   Read: OTP_EMAIL_INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md

